name: Lost & Found Music Studios
overview: Teen singers-songwriters in an elite music program form bonds of friendship, creativity and romance while turning their passion into their profession.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: In this elite music program, young musicians perfect their craft while handling the trials of teen life: crushes, competition and fitting in.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: Rachel gets a record deal. Clara exhibits strange behavior that brings up unresolved issues from the past for John. Luke and Leia reach an agreement.

episodes.name: Lost and Found
episodes.overview: A party is thrown for the graduates going on tour, And somebody gets the wrong idea when their crush preforms a love song written by another band member.

episodes.name: See Through Me
episodes.overview: Leia is miffed when best friend Rachel's song is picked over hers for use in the upcoming auditions. Eva helps Jude find a theme for his music video.

episodes.name: Play the Record
episodes.overview: Mr. T helps the band record a demo. A dancer who wants to sing, a kid from a rough neighborhood and a small-town songwriter are invited to audition.

episodes.name: Heart & Soul
episodes.overview: The first day of auditions include a singer who tried out the year before, a pianist smothered by his stage mom and a girl who learned the wrong song.

episodes.name: Invincible
episodes.overview: One auditioner wants to break the rules. Clara's nerves take over. Isaac shows off his stage presence. John fights to give Annabelle a second chance.

episodes.name: All About the Music
episodes.overview: The veterans give the newbies a tour. Leia worries when a new girl hits it off with Luke. Mary pushes Eva to go beyond her comfort zone.

episodes.name: Day After Day
episodes.overview: John tries to conceal his new "living situation" from Michelle. Clara must confront her insecurities when she suffers a bad bout of stage fright.

episodes.name: Dancing in the Rain
episodes.overview: A celebrity visit ignites a heated rivalry between Jude and Rachel. Annabelle tries to establish herself as a member of the in crowd.

episodes.name: Potent Love
episodes.overview: Isaac and Jude find a mysterious songbook. Maggie, Leia, Rachel and Annabelle forge deeper bonds when they decide to share secrets.

episodes.name: Heart Shape
episodes.overview: Leia's first date goes awry. John and Luke decide to visit their old piano teacher. Jude tries to help Eva by setting up a private recording session.

episodes.name: Freebird
episodes.overview: To impress her peers, Clara lies about being the writer of a song she performs at Open Stage. John must face a fear when Luke gives him an ultimatum.

episodes.name: Sunrise
episodes.overview: Leia's diva demands threaten Maggie's chance to open for a popular band. Isaac worries when his shady brother starts hanging around the studio.

episodes.name: Callin' Callin' Part 1
episodes.overview: Eva shows Clara a way to redeem herself. Maggie breaks her Luke truce with Leia. Michelle overhears John's true feelings for her during band practice.

episodes.name: Callin' Callin' Part 2
episodes.overview: Michelle has a uplifting conversation with Johns grandmother. The bands first gig, isn't going as hoped.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: In this elite music program, young musicians perfect their craft while handling the trials of teen life: crushes, competition and fitting in.

episodes.name: Sweet Tarts
episodes.overview: Maggie rejoins the girls' band but refuses to accept Leia's controlling ways. Mary coaches Theo to turn his mediocre song into a truly heartfelt one.

episodes.name: Rhythm in My Heartbeat
episodes.overview: When Leia's plan to fix Luke's van backfires, she blames Rachel. Michelle creatively reveals her feelings to John. Eva rebels against her strict mom.

episodes.name: Wondering
episodes.overview: Mr. T gives Eva's mom blunt advice. John and Michelle struggle to understand each other. Family responsibilities interfere with Mary's songwriting.

episodes.name: Take Control
episodes.overview: Rachel gets an unexpected offer from a record label. Jude finds Clara difficult to work with. Luke's opinions flow too freely during an interview.

episodes.name: Hit My Heart
episodes.overview: John agrees to write a pop song for Michelle's dance competition. Rachel has a secret admirer. Isaac worries about a bad influence on his brother.

episodes.name: How Far We've Come
episodes.overview: Isaac takes drastic measures to keep Tully away from Lost & Found, hurting Mary in the process. John and Michelle get bad advice from their friends.

episodes.name: Last Shot
episodes.overview: A competition requires the girls' band to swap a member with the boys' band. Against Parker's advice, Jude auditions for a commercial.

episodes.name: Take You There
episodes.overview: Annabelle taps Nate's talent for making ringtones that match an individual's personality. Thoughts of Tully distract Mary from an important audition.

episodes.name: Let It Go
episodes.overview: Leia tries to make Luke jealous. When Rachel unknowingly leaks her song online, her record label has a surprising reaction. John worries about Clara.

episodes.name: Falling for You
episodes.overview: Longing to experience her first kiss, Eva seeks Jude's advice. Rachel adjusts to her new BFF. Luke asks Theo to distract him from thoughts of Leia.

episodes.name: Call My Name
episodes.overview: Annabelle devises a plan to bring harmony back to the girls' band. When Mary tries to cheer Isaac up on his birthday, he makes a confession to her.

episodes.name: You Could Have it All
episodes.overview: When Clara cracks under her own pressure to perfect some demos for Music Week, John draws on a painful experience to help her. Eva tries a new look.

episodes.name: The Sound of Change
episodes.overview: When Maggie gets good news, Theo reacts oddly. Convinced he made things worse for Clara, John pushes Michelle away. Luke gives Leia a surprise.

2.overview: Rachel gets a record deal. Clara exhibits strange behavior that brings up unresolved issues from the past for John. Luke and Leia reach an agreement.
